article.headline: Saint Mary's 80, San Diego St. 58
article.story: MORAGA, Calif. -- Mickey McConnell scored a career-high 24 points, Omar Samhan added 17 points and 16 rebounds and St. Mary's beat San Diego State 80-58 on Monday night. Freshman Matthew Dellavedova had 17 points and four rebounds for the Gaels, who lost to the Aztecs in the NIT quarterfinals last year. Malcolm Thomas had 14 points and eight rebounds for San Diego State.
